    <main>
        <h2>Learn About Bullying</h2>
        <article>
            <h3>What is Bullying?</h3>
            <p>Bullying is unwanted, aggressive behavior among school-aged children that involves a real or perceived power imbalance...</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h3>How to Prevent Bullying</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Speak up when you see bullying</li>
                <li>Support victims and encourage inclusion</li>
                <li>Educate yourself and others</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
        <article>
            <h3>Videos & Guides</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.stopbullying.gov/" target="_blank">StopBullying.gov</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.pacer.org/bullying/" target="_blank">PACER's National Bullying Prevention Center</a></li>
            </ul>
